tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE impact_ai_decisions (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   decision_name TEXT,
   impact_level TEXT,
   societal_group TEXT,
   ethical_analysis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ethical_analysis_report (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   report_id INT,
   decision_id INT,
   group_id INT,
   analysis_result TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE impact_of_ai_decisions (
    decision_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    decision_description TEXT,
    impact TEXT,
    societal_group TEXT
)
